<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Pa Ka Mukit Tai</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa hih ka hetma chun,
 Midang Pathien ahim ka tii;
 A chanchin pha ka vak sim leh,
 Ka pa, ka mansak kha ahi.

[V2]
 Ka manna lauhuma ei hawlna chu,
 Gimtheih tincheng A hung thuoka;
 Ka thagau hukdam na di'n

[V3]
 2. A chanchin vak gen zieng hin le,
 Lunggil a sukipak ngei aw;
 Thagau a hetsakna vang chun,
 Mitthi a luong lo thei puoi.
 A bukima muh chu ka nuom ngei aw,
 Ka gitloh thienna ding thisan
 A luonna pawn ngei kha le.

[V4]
 3. A thih ding kuon khan le Isu,
 A melmate di'n A paucham;
 &quot;He pa, amau hi ngaidam in,
 A thilhih a he puou&quot; tin.
 Hehpihna a le a tawpkhawk ngei ie!
 Pathien hehpihna Kalvari;
 Khela genthei a um puou.

[V5]
 4. Mi gilo keihaw a dingin,
 Na kipie zo ngei ie Isu!
 Na silhpuon le na chang puo maw?
 Na puonak di'n phun a san ui.
 Hinna pie khawp hiel a ei Hehpihpa,
 Ka thih ding kuon chanin Lalpa;
 Lungin hun ngilh hiel puong ka.</lyrics>
<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
<hymn_number>79</hymn_number>
</song>